text: Ifeanyi Ifeanyi (born 15 August 1995) is a Nigerian international footballer who plays for Mash'al Mubarek, as a midfielder. ==Career== Born in Lagos, Ifeanyi has played club football for MFM and Akwa United. In January 2019 he moved to Algerian club ES Sétif.
